Genre : Action, RPG

Rebel Galaxyis a swashbuckling space adventure,  with action-packed
combat, exploration, discovery,  trade, and  negotiation  with  the
outlandish denizens  at the  edge of  the known  universe.  As  the
commander of an immensely  powerful star  destroyer,  youll  battle
pirates,  explore  anomalies,  befriend  aliens,   scavenge  battle
wreckage, mine asteroids, and discover artifacts.

For more info go to : http://www.gog.com/game/rebel_galaxy
